### HTML -> XHTML

Find:
	<(img|input|link|hr|br|meta)((\s+\w+(\s*=\s*(?:".*?"|'.*?'|[^'">\s]+))?)+\s*|\s*)>
Replace: 
	<$1$2 />

### LanguageUtil -> bean

Find:
	<%= LanguageUtil.get\(pageContext, "([A-Za-z0-9_-]+)"\) %>

Replace:
	<bean:message key="$1" />

### Single quoted bean -> Double quoted bean

Find:
	'(<bean:message key="([A-Za-z0-9_-]+)" />)'
Replace:
	"$1"